0:00:00.040,0:00:04.040
Wakadii? Iwe  mazuva ako ekutevera akamira.

0:00:04.040,0:00:04.960
Hongu

0:00:04.960,0:00:06.280
Ne mhaka ye mapiritsi.

0:00:06.280,0:00:07.680
Hongu.

0:00:07.680,0:00:10.960
Hungu, Munhu waMwari. Ari pane madhiragi;  anotora zvinodhaka.

0:00:10.960,0:00:13.320
Ndizvo zvandiri kutaura. Ini ndati, nekuda kwe madhiragi.

0:00:13.320,0:00:15.420
Hongu, Munhu waMwari. Akapindwa muropa ne madhiragi.

0:00:15.420,0:00:17.240
- Akapindwa muropa nezvinodhaka? - Hungu, Munhu waMwari.

0:00:17.240,0:00:22.120
Izvi zvakakanganisa kuenda kwake kumwedzi nekumupa kutemwa ne musoro nguva dzose.

0:00:22.120,0:00:26.140
Hongu, Munhu waMwari. Ichokwadi. Ndauya naye. Ishamwari ye mwanasikana wangu.

0:00:26.140,0:00:28.020
Zvakanaka. Huya kuno.

0:00:28.020,0:00:32.220
Kununurwa MuZita raJesu

0:00:32.220,0:00:34.580
Poreswa, muzita raJesu!

0:00:34.580,0:00:37.420
Kununurwa MuZita raJesu

0:00:37.420,0:00:39.860
Asununguka.

0:00:39.860,0:00:45.440
Mushure mekununurwa kwake shure kwehuporofita, mukadzi wacho akatanga kuenda kumwedzi

0:00:45.440,0:00:49.380
uye akadzoka zuva raitevera kuti apupure.

0:00:49.380,0:01:07.800
Anoenda kuchimbudzi

0:01:07.800,0:01:20.140
Kusaenda Ku Mwedzi Kwaive Kwamira  Kunotanga Kuerera Shure Kwe Huprofita

0:01:20.140,0:01:24.960
HUCHAPUPU HUNOENDERERA

0:01:24.960,0:01:28.200
Emanueri! (Mwari Anesu - Mateo 1:23)

0:01:28.200,0:01:30.840
Rumbidzai Ishe!

0:01:30.840,0:01:33.320
Zita rangu ndi Hawa Nakamba.

0:01:33.320,0:01:35.600
Ini ndinobva kuZambia.

0:01:35.600,0:01:43.940
Vanhu vakamira pedyo neni ndi mai vangu, tete vangu ne mukoma wangu.

0:01:43.940,0:01:53.460
Vhiki yapera musi we Svondo apo ndakauya, mu Porofita akaporofita kwandiri kuti ndakanga ndarega kuenda kumwedzi

0:01:53.460,0:02:01.660
nemhaka ye kutora madhiragi uye kuti ini ndairwadziwa nemusoro nekuda kwe zvinodhaka.

0:02:01.660,0:02:06.340
Ndinosimbisa kuti uporofita hwaive hwechokwadi chizere.

0:02:06.340,0:02:09.220
Hareruya!

0:02:09.220,0:02:17.480
Izvo zvose zvakatanga makore matatu apfuura apo ndakange ndakapindwa muropa ne zvinodhaka kuZambia.

0:02:17.480,0:02:19.660
Ndainwa kodhini.

0:02:19.660,0:02:27.140
Pazuva, ndaigona kunwa mabhodhoro 5 kana kusvika ku6 ekodhini.

0:02:27.140,0:02:38.240
Apo shamwari dzangu dzaigona kungotora bhodhoro rimwe chete kana maviri ekodhini, ndaigona kunwa mabhodhoro 6.

0:02:38.240,0:02:44.120
Ndinotenda Mwari nokuti izvo kodhini  yaindiita kuti ndiite,

0:02:44.120,0:02:47.680
yandiita kuti ndisatye chero munhu.

0:02:47.680,0:02:54.840
Ndaiwanzoba mari yamai vangu kuti nditenge kodhini.

0:02:54.840,0:03:00.520
Ndaizovatyisidzira kana vasina kundipa mari.

0:03:00.520,0:03:03.820
"Amai, ndipei mari ndinoda kuenda kunoita chimwe chinhu."

0:03:03.820,0:03:05.960
Ndaigona kunyange kuvabira.

0:03:05.960,0:03:15.000
Ndinotenda Mwari. Apo mu Porofita akandibata musi we Svondo, ndakanunurwa uye ndasununguka ikozvino.

0:03:15.000,0:03:20.600
Apo mu Porofita akandibata, ndakanzwa chimwe chinhu chichifamba famba (mumuviri wangu).

0:03:20.600,0:03:22.340
Ndakanzwa kurerukirwa.

0:03:22.340,0:03:30.440
Titaurire muchidimbu zvaikonzereswa ne madhiragi awainwa kare mumuviri wako ne hutano hwako.

0:03:30.440,0:03:34.180
Mushure mekutora madhiragi aya, ndakarega kutevera mazuva angu.

0:03:34.180,0:03:37.960
Ndakanga ndisina han'a kana kuteerera kune ani zvake.

0:03:37.960,0:03:42.160
Apo mu Porofita akangondibata, paakandinyengeterera,

0:03:42.160,0:03:47.380
pakarepo mushure maizvozvo, ndakabva ndatanga kuenda kumwedzi.

0:03:47.380,0:03:48.160
Ameni.

0:03:48.160,0:03:52.960
Hawa Nakamba Ne Mhuri Huchapupu hwe Huporofita

0:03:52.960,0:04:01.260
Ndangariro dzangu dzakadzoka zvakare. Ndakavata zvakanaka uye ndinonzwa kurerukirwa, mushure mokunge mu Porofita andinamatira.

0:04:01.260,0:04:07.260
Ndinonzwa ndakarerukirwa uye ndava nani iye zvino. Ndasununguka. Ndinokutendai, Jesu.

0:04:07.260,0:04:12.120
Nhomba ye madhiragi, ne zvose zve mararamiro acho zvakaenda?

0:04:12.120,0:04:14.020
Zvakaenda.

0:04:14.020,0:04:19.940
Izvi ndizvo zvakaitika shure kwekunge munhu waMwari andinamatira.

0:04:19.940,0:04:24.480
Ndakanga ndisina kutevera kwenguva refu kwazvo.

0:04:24.480,0:04:35.160
Asi pakarepo mushure mekunge munhu waMwari andinamatira, ndakatanga.

0:04:35.160,0:04:36.440
Ndinokutendai, Jesu Kristu.

0:04:36.440,0:04:39.040
Tiri kuona zvechokwadi kuti hanzvadzi yedu yanunurwa.

0:04:39.040,0:04:42.200
Takaona mushoko iroro reuporofita apo munhu waMwari akataura naye,

0:04:42.200,0:04:46.740
iye akanga achiri pasi pesimba remadhiragi; akanga asingakwanisi kunyange kuzvibata  kuti apindure.

0:04:46.740,0:04:51.820
Asi nhasi, ndangariro dzake dzadzoserwa, kuenda kwake kumwedzi kwadzoserwa, kupindwa muropa ne madhiragi kwaenda

0:04:51.820,0:04:54.380
uye ari pano nemhuri yake kugovera uchapupu hunoshamisa.

0:04:54.380,0:05:01.000
Hanzvadzi, yambiro yako ku vanhu ndeipi, kunyanya vechidiki pasi rose vari kukuona?

0:05:01.000,0:05:08.480
Yambiro yangu inoenda kune vechidiki vose varikundiona pasi rose.

0:05:08.480,0:05:11.880
Regai kutora madhiragi, hazvina kunaka.

0:05:11.880,0:05:17.460
Huyai kuna Mwari, Anogona kukuporesai nekushandura hupenyu hwenyu.

0:05:17.460,0:05:18.300
Ameni.

0:05:18.300,0:05:23.400
